Changes between 0.0.1 and 0.0.2
	- Events added to the API: xd_grab_events and xd_next_event.
	- Docks now can be moved and reordered with the mouse.
	- Corrected a bug that might cause the server to segfault when sending
	a XPM.
	- Corrected a bug that caused a invalid protocol error when sending a
	color variable as 0xFF.
	- Two new applets were included: xdevent (a tutorial applet) and xdchess.

Changes between birth and 0.0.1
	- Initial release.
